    {
      "id": "PopularPost90450",
      "post_content": "There's one reason that Megrim is better than this- my friends may hate my blue/black Megrim deck (which demolishes through any number of opponents in multiplayer) but they would never allow me to play said deck with four of this instead... do you want the world to hate you on turn two, or three? In a one-on-one, though, there is no doubt that this card is superior.",
